08/08/2010
ZAGREB, Croatia -- The police announced on Saturday (August 7th) they will press charges against two people for an attack on a Croatian HTV crew during Victory and Homeland Thanksgiving Day celebrations. The journalists from the public broadcaster were insulted and stoned during the event, held on Thursday in the village of Cavoglave. The Croatian Journalists' Association condemned the incident. (HRT, Nova TV, Hina, tportal.hr - 07/08/10)
